        With this package, it is easy to modify the GeeXboX in a few seconds without having to build the sources. The generator produces an ISO image of the GeeXboX, ready to be burned on disc. This piece of software currently works under both GNU/Linux and Microsoft Windows 9x/NT/2k/XP systems.<br/><br/>
          <b><use name="dl-x86-gen"/> - <use name="dl1-x86-gen"/> - <use name="dl2-x86-gen"/> - 8.2 MB</b>
          <br/>
          <b><use name="dl-ppc-gen"/> - <use name="dl1-ppc-gen"/> - <use name="dl2-ppc-gen"/> - 8.5 MB</b>
      </content>
